Description: Matrix Creator kernel modules for Raspberry Pi OS Bookworm
 This package provides DKMS source for MATRIX Creator kernel modules
 optimized for Raspberry Pi OS Bookworm (Debian 12.12).
 .
 Supports:
  - Raspberry Pi 5 with 6.12.47+rpt-rpi-2712 kernel (ARM64)
  - Raspberry Pi 4 with 6.1.70-rpi-v8 kernel (ARM64)
 .
 The package includes kernel modules for:
  - Core MFD functionality (matrixio-core)
  - Audio codec support (matrixio-codec, matrixio-mic, matrixio-playback)
  - Environmental sensors (matrixio-env, matrixio-imu)
  - LED ring control (matrixio-everloop)
  - GPIO interface (matrixio-gpio)
  - UART interface (matrixio-uart)
  - Register map interface (matrixio-regmap)